creator: William Cooper Nell
description:
LibriVox recording of The Colored Patriots of the American Revolution by William Cooper Nell.
Read in English by progressingamerica
A study of the black patriots of the American Revolution, with introductions by Harriet Beecher Stowe and Wendell Phillips.
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
